Source: ros-hydro-rosbridge-suite
Section: misc
Priority: extra
Maintainer: "Brandon Alexander <baalexander@gmail.com>, Jihoon Lee <jihoonlee.in@gmail.com>, Russell Toris <rctoris@wpi.edu>"
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7.0.50~), ros-hydro-catkin
Homepage: https://github.com/RobotWebTools/rosbridge_suite
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: ros-hydro-rosbridge-suite
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ros-hydro-rosapi, ros-hydro-rosbridge-library, ros-hydro-rosbridge-server
Description: Rosbridge provides a JSON API to ROS functionality for non-ROS programs. There are a variety of front ends that interface with rosbridge, including a WebSocket server for web browsers to interact with. Rosbridge_suite is a meta-package containing rosbridge, various front end packages for rosbridge like a WebSocket package, and helper packages.
